@startuml
actor User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Notes API" as API
participant "File Storage" as FS
database "Notes DB" as DB
participant "Version Service" as Version
participant "Sync Service" as Sync

User -> UI: 1. Выбрать .txt файл
UI -> UI: 2. Валидация (.txt)
UI -> API: 3. POST /api/notes (file, metadata)
activate API

API -> FS: 4. Сохранить файл (file)
activate FS
FS --> API: 5. file_url
deactivate FS

API -> DB: 6. INSERT notes (user_id, file_url, title...)
activate DB
DB --> API: 7. note_id
deactivate DB

API -> Version: 8. POST /api/versions (note_id, file_url, comment="v1")
activate Version
Version --> API: 9. 201 Created
deactivate Version

API -> Sync: 10. Send event "NoteCreated" (note_id, user_id)
activate Sync
Sync --> API: 11. Event accepted
deactivate Sync

API --> UI: 12. 201 Created, note_id
deactivate API
UI --> User: 13. Показать сообщение "Заметка создана и поставлена в очередь на синхронизацию"
@enduml